        'Dark washes are your friend — they create a streamlined, continuous line from waist to ankle. Avoid whiskering, fading, or heavy distressing across the thigh area, which draws the eye to the widest point. Specific picks: Levi\'s Ribcage Bootcut (high waist with a leg-lengthening flare), Citizens of Humanity Paloma Baggy (relaxed through the hip with a modern wide leg), and Madewell Perfect Vintage Wide-Leg (comfortable stretch with a dark, clean wash). For a sleek everyday option, the Spanx Straight Leg Jean offers smoothing compression that pear shapes often appreciate without feeling restrictive.',
